overview:
The Factory Interactive is fueled by a passion for developing strong, beautiful and enduring messages conceived through a marriage of design and technology. At the core, The Factory Interactive team are explorers of possibility and architects of memory. The Factory Interactive designers create rich, immersive experiences that increase message retention and reward the audience. The Factory Interactive gives personality to product, which results in a stronger, more effective brand. The Factory Interactive looks toward the horizon for fresh technological innovations and advancements that will provide clients the competitive advantage needed in today’s global marketplace.

We are the generation who grew up with an Atari and now own the Xbox. We don’t ‘surf’ the internet, but rather, help to define it. The web does not stop at six o’clock for us, it rides shotgun in our conversations, integrates into our daily lives and, more often than not, keeps us awake at night. We continually challenge ourselves in order to remain fresh, creative, knowledgeable ambassadors of the mediums that have become a part of our daily routines. It is this passion and our core beliefs in what we do that is manifested in every project we undertake.
